snippet.title: Colin Mcrae Rally - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Colin Mcrae Rally - PC Gameplay

Subscribe here ►►► http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=FirstPlaysHD
Also SHARE, COMMENT, LIKE ☺

Colin McRae Rally is the first game in the Colin McRae Rally series, released in January 1998 by Codemasters in Europe, and in February 2000 in North America on the PC and PlayStation, and in September 2001 on the Game Boy Color. It features 8 official cars (and their drivers) and rallies from the 1998 World Rally Championship season, in addition to 4 extra cars.


░▒▓ PC Hardware ▓▒░

CPU: Intel Core i7 3770K @ 4.20 Ghz
RAM: 8 GB
GPU: ASUS GTX760-DC2OC-2GD5
OS:  Windows 7 64bit


░▒▓ Recording HW ▓▒░
